------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product optionally interoperates with the following third-party
software at runtime (not bundled):

  - Claude Code CLI (Anthropic)
      Driven as a subprocess when `agent.provider: claude_code` is set.
      Sinfonia does not redistribute the CLI. Users must install and
      authenticate it independently.

  - Codex CLI (OpenAI)
      Driven as a subprocess when `agent.provider: codex` is set.
      Sinfonia does not redistribute the CLI. Users must install and
      authenticate it independently.

  - Ollama (https://ollama.com)
      Optional locally hosted model server contacted over HTTP when
      `agent.provider: ollama` is set.

  - Linear (https://linear.app), Atlassian Jira (https://www.atlassian.com)
      Issue trackers contacted over their public APIs. Sinfonia uses
      operator-supplied credentials and respects the access scopes of
      those credentials.

